name: Robo-Robbery
description:
Made for Wowie Jam 4.0 - The theme was "Cooperate with AI"

Nikki and Pathr are in the process of stealing money from a mysterious facility. Help Pathr reach the end of the level while collecting all of the money on his way.

All art by me, SFX are from FreeSound.org, and music is "Bleeps and Bloops" by  Dream Protocol
